data.description: Welcome home to this contemporary 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 1 car garage townhouse in Hagerstown! Newer subdivision in the city... Only steps to the amenity filled Pangborn Park. Open layout with walkout basement and plenty of space for entertaining. One car garage with bonus EV charger.  Great, main level living with large eat in kitchen with island and slider to private deck. Nice floors in the living and dining room with a charming bay window and half bath. 3 miles to Meritus Hospital. 4 miles to Hagerstown Community College... Hop, skip and a jump to I-70  and I-81 for Frederick or Pennsylvania/WV. Great central location close to City Hall, National Theater and Hagerstown City Park. Take advantage of the lowering interest rates and submit your offer!
